1101
01:16:50,364 --> 01:16:52,099
Jak to vypadá?

1102
01:16:52,199 --> 01:16:54,368
Zlomenina nad loktem, kapitáne.

1103
01:16:54,468 --> 01:16:56,303
Musím to srovnat.

1104
01:16:56,403 --> 01:16:57,636
Tak do toho.

